1. Include jquery.input_suggestion.js to your applicable /javascripts/ directory

2. Setup your in your applicable application.js file or wherever your please:
$(document).ready(function(){
  initInputSuggestion();
});

3. Setup your input field defaults wherever you please
  <input name="pirate[name]" data-suggestion-text="Yarr Doe" />
  - or -
  = pirate_form.input :name, 'data-suggestion-text' => 'Yarr Doe'

4. Setup a style input.suggestion_text in your appropriate css for mo' cool effect:
   input.suggestion_text {
    color: #ccc;
   }
   